Tue Jan  3 19:05:42 2012  Naohisa Goto  <ngotogenome@gmail.com>

	* include/ruby/defines.h (FLUSH_REGISTER_WINDOWS): move sparc asm code
	  to a separete file sparc.c for preventing inlining optimization.
