Wed Jul 27 01:13:00 2011  Kenta Murata  <mrkn@mrkn.jp>

	* ext/bigdecimal/lib/bigdecimal/util.rb (Rational#to_d):
	  zero or negative precision is error.  fixes #5098.
	  [ruby-dev:44210]

